headline.main: England Stuns US Women 1-0 in SheBelieves Cup Soccer
headline.print_headline: England Stuns US Women 1-0 in SheBelieves Cup Soccer

lead_paragraph: While Jill Ellis never wants to see the United States women's soccer team lose a game, the coach believes good things can come out of a setback, especially in an event without a major prize.
